<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="why-brainblog">Why “Brain&nbsp;Blog”?<a href="https://tchez.github.io/brain-blog/blog/welcome#why-brainblog" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Why “Brain&nbsp;Blog”?" title="Direct link to Why “Brain&nbsp;Blog”?">​</a></h3>
<blockquote>
<p><em>“When we teach, we learn twice.”</em><br>
<!-- -->— Translated from Paulo Freire</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Brain&nbsp;Blog is a public backup of my brain where I capture study notes,
organise references and document learning journeys.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="content-structure">Content structure<a href="https://tchez.github.io/brain-blog/blog/welcome#content-structure" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Content structure" title="Direct link to Content structure">​</a></h3>
